Package cz.cvut.fel.omo.smarthome.room

Class RoomDirector

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.omo.smarthome.room.RoomDirector
public final class RoomDirector extends Object
Class is responsible for directing the construction of rooms using a RoomBuilder and various other components. It follows the Singleton pattern and provides a single instance for coordinating the building process of different room types. This class abstracts the construction details and allows for the creation of rooms with specific characteristics based on their types.
